{
  "3035090": {
    "name": "Popcorn Fever",
    "steam_appid": 3035090,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/7403972811bb18ffb01f627c7b115ecd.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=333 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/aad9092f144ac92370c24936ae4f9ce7.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >需要喝杯咖啡放松一下，长途旅行中无聊，或者只是想打发时间？开始一局游戏，尽可能地合并爆米花吧！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>瞄准、释放并合并</strong> 爆米花来获得积分。<strong>个性化你的游戏</strong>，解锁独特且惊喜的能力。找到自己的风格，进入 <strong>排行榜</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能登顶顶级玩家的神殿吗？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/ff4af78a27374b8350e3371bb91b2c08.poster.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/ff4af78a27374b8350e3371bb91b2c08.webm?t=1763389966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/db60e0c107289dd1dbfffea9970c65a1.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/077a9f3e469236c33df66336d611c1dc.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏目标很简单！合并两个相同的爆米花来将它们结合并获得积分。爆米花越大，积分越高。通过移动角色来将爆米花放置在理想的位置，并利用物理效果为你所用！游戏过程中有11种可爱符号等待你去发现。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>交换</strong>：你可以随时将当前符号与下一个符号交换！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>连击</strong>：连续的合并会通过连击计数器提高积分倍数！如果掉落的符号没有迅速形成合并，连击计数器的积分会被收集。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/4bbbcbdbc31b2df33538dd8956e3d5a8.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/530a11eb003c413cc7ec08b5d8ba24e3.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在商店中选择你的魔力；总共有9种魔力可以发现。魔力通过合并爆米花来充能。当倒计时归零时，它们就可以使用了。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>孵化</strong>：所有的爆米花粒都会变成“普通”爆米花！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/24dd0dd3b090a2628116f7f357174fcd.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>摇晃</strong>：袋子会左右摇晃，帮助你创造新的合并机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/d5b3cb1062c7a6e1427bb4f8916f193e.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>爆米花雨</strong>：爆米花粒从天而降！这是你创造大量合并的机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/7ad8cf05fa113d11db1b6688f4c37d80.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>连击x2</strong>：连击计数器的积分翻倍！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/ce7a67b67ab80074d5541879fcce57ab.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发薪日</strong>：“金爆”会出现在你的游戏中！免费使用它，尽情享受吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/0e56b644afdd55e9cc28e983845775cd.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>炸弹</strong>：点燃的炸弹掉落时会爆炸，摧毁周围的符号。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/7bad0a5301b63bd127a4b226b36e9900.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>火球</strong>：火球无法控制，会弹跳并摧毁它接触的符号，然后消失。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/0ee9cbf9d8709141e0ba628401a3f646.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>魔法师</strong>：强大但不可预测，魔法师可以提升多个符号。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/a2b0c9de7052b00e2187b4e50d6e44d5.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小丑</strong>：小巧但强大，小丑爆米花会进化它接触到的第一个符号。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/edf5ca1788374b546c0eb40521e23706.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/2436251a551b930cc1b6577d511ac364.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/86a55fd56afdf08b4727616429a13de9.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以购买物品来个性化你的角色、袋子或游戏背景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你也可以选择装备你最喜欢的两个能力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/d01e730ff93a830f34d1b439844f3501.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/1c9bcca2d0a19771827a6f2045440a94.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >排行榜分为两种：个人最高分和全球排行榜，包括每日、每周、每月和总榜！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/def645324fd76f5ef6a6343d4ff5e7de.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的角色会自动旋转爆米花；有时候你需要等待合适的时机来巧妙放置符号！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爆米花粒“Poppy”小而密集，可以随处穿梭。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合并两个神圣的爆米花会带来惊喜，你能发现它吗？</p></li></ul>",
